何。经济援助和奖学金适用于资格的学生”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3842500" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3842500" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3842500" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Edward-Berthelot_GC-Images.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Edward-Berthelot_GC-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Edward-Berthelot_GC-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Edward-Berthelot_GC-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Edward-Berthelot_GC-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Edward-Berthelot_GC-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Edward-Berthelot_GC-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3842500" class="wp-caption-text">坎耶·韦斯特。学分：爱德华·伯特洛（Edward Berthelot）/GC图像</figcaption></figure><p>在韦斯特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanyes-twitter-and-instagram-accounts-locked-after-antisemitic-posts-3325446">在2022年10月首次臭名昭著的反犹太蒂拉德（Tirade）</a>之后，这很快就陷入了争议。在其他许多古怪的说法中，他告诉他需要<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-tells-jewish-people-to-forgive-hitler-compares-porn-to-the-holocaust-3361860">“原谅希特勒”</a>为大屠杀而“原谅希特勒”  - <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-apologises-jewish-community-antisemitic-comments-3563267">他在2023年为回来道歉</a>。在讲话之后，各个家庭开始将孩子从学校里拉出来。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-threatened-to-cage-donda-academy-students-new-lawsuit-claims-3612681">去年由西部的前雇员特雷弗·菲利普斯（Trevor Phillips）提起了另一项诉讼</a>。在此案中，他指责西部有许多爆炸性指控，包括口头虐待，威胁身体暴力并将自己与希特勒进行比较。</p><p>正如包括<a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/kanye-west-donda-academy-lawsuit-kids-cages-shave-heads-rcna145966" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>NBC新闻</em></a>， <a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/kanye-west-lawsuit-donda-school-1234997814/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石</em></a>和<a href="https://consequence.net/2024/04/kanye-west-donda-academy-cage-students/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>后果</em></a>在内的各种媒体所强调的那样，菲利普斯声称韦斯特告诉学生，他想剃光头并将其锁在笼子里。他还声称说唱歌手经常称赞希特勒，甚至一次将自己与纳粹领导人进行了比较。</p><p> 2月，托马斯·朗（Thomas Long）法官命令韦斯特（West）支付2,560美元的罚款，并在4月30日不迟于4月30日待命，但由于韦斯特（West）的律师爱德华多·马托雷尔（Eduardo Martorell）表示，他无法保证与说唱歌手的交流，因此无法确定约会。 “我的客户不是那么合理。正如<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/kanye-west-sanctions-lawsuit-antisemitic-tirades-1235274166/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石乐队</em></a>报道的那样，他说。</p><p>海莉（Hailey）和拜尔斯（Byers）是2023年首位诉讼的前唐纳学院（Donda Academy）的工作人员，声称学生在学习中“至少落后两年”。同时，米克斯（Meeks）指责西部禁止填字游戏和着色表，禁止使用硬椅使用，并坚持在一楼举行所有班级，因为他“据说害怕楼梯”。</p><p>所有的老师都声称，当他们告诉学校的领导他们的担忧时，他们被不公平地解雇了。 </p><figure id="attachment_3840227" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3840227" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3840227" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-5.jpg" alt="坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）参加了第67届年度格莱美奖" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-5.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-5-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-5-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-5-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-5-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-5-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3840227" class="wp-caption-text">坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）参加了第67届年度格莱美奖。学分：录音学院的Matt Winkelmeyer/Getty Image</figcaption></figure><p>近几个月来，韦斯特（West）因在他的网站上出售<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-releases-new-song-beauty-and-the-beast-before-stripping-yeezy-site-to-only-sell-swastika-t-shirt-3836729">胸部上有大巨大的swastika标志的白色T恤而</a>受到抨击，这可能是对“ Heil Hitler” Chant的参考。</p><p>该网站<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shopify-shut-down-kanye-wests-yeezy-website-for-selling-swastika-t-shirt-matthew-koma-responds-with-fuck-ye-merch-3837155">后来被Shopify取消</a>，尽管在线零售商后来<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shopify-says-kanye-wests-site-was-removed-over-fraud-potential-not-swastika-t-shirt-3837621">表示，由于欺诈的可能性，艺术家的网站被取消了 - 不是因为它出售了Swastika T恤</a>。 Shopify确实谴责了该物品，称其为“卑鄙，令人作呕和不可原谅”。</p><p>韦斯特然后去X（以前是Twitter）说他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-had-swastika-t-shirt-idea-for-over-eight-years-3838835">有“八年多”的T恤的想法</a>。 It came alongside a <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-is-never-apologising-for-my-jewish-comments-and-claims-to-have-dominion-over-bianca-censori-fuck-all-that-woke-shit-3835994">string of highly controversial posts</a> which saw him <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-is-never-apologising-for-my-jewish-comments-and-claims-to-have-dominion-over-bianca-censori-fuck-all-that-woke-shit-3835994">rescind his apology to the Jewish community for his past anti-Semitic remarks</a> , and go on to declare himself “a Nazi” and write: “I love Hitler”, as well as praise billionaire and X owner <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/elon-musk">Elon Musk</a> as “the most lit person that [has] ever been on Twitter”, following <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/elon-musk-sparks-backlash-with-nazi-like-gesture-at-trump-inauguration-3830625">the latter&#39;s accusations of Nazism at Donald Trump&#39;s presidential inauguration</a> .</p><p>然后，这位备受争议的说唱歌手似乎回避了他先前的评论， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-has-come-to-the-realisation-that-hes-not-a-nazi-after-reflection-3839623">X带着X分享“进一步反思”，他“意识到我不是纳粹”</a> 。但是， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-is-producing-more-swastika-apparel-after-claiming-hes-not-a-nazi-3840479">仅几天后，他的X页面上出现了更多的swastika服装</a>。</p><p>上述帖子大肆宣传看到<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-wests-x-account-has-been-deactivated-after-bizarre-weekend-rant-3836418">他的X帐户被删除并停用了</a>，后来证实说唱歌手已<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-dropped-by-talent-agency-following-anti-semitic-posts-3837245">被他的人才机构放弃，</a>他的前任参谋长辞去了Yeezy Company。</p><p>他在二月份的狂暴还看到他参加了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-is-never-apologising-for-my-jewish-comments-and-claims-to-have-dominion-over-bianca-censori-fuck-all-that-woke-shit-3835994">妻子比安卡·辛索里（Bianca Censori）</a>参加格莱美岛红地毯活动后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-2025-kanye-west-shows-up-with-wife-bianca-censori-who-reveals-shocking-see-through-dress-3833867">她穿着一件透明的连衣裙，露出了她赤裸的身材</a>。他还发布了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-voices-support-for-diddy-and-chris-brown-free-puff-3835815">一系列推文，以支持迪迪（Diddy）和克里斯·布朗（Chris Brown），并敦促前者在性虐待指控中被释放</a>。</p><p>自从社交媒体上咆哮以来，坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kanye-west-ty-dolla-sign-vultures-1-review-lyrics-tracklist-3585917">“秃鹰”</a>合作者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ty-dolla-ign-condemns-hate-speech-following-kanye-wests-anti-semitic-posts-and-swastika-t-shirt-controversy-3837549">ty dolla $ ign谴责了他的仇恨言论</a>，查理·普拉（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charlie-puth-begs-kanye-west-to-stop-promoting-incredibly-dangerous-messages-and-swastika-tee-3837062">Charlie Puth）恳求韦斯特（Charlie Puth）停止推广“令人难以置信的危险”信息，</a>而<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/friends"><em>朋友</em></a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/david-schwimmer-calls-for-action-against-kanye-west-after-nazi-comments-silence-is-complicity-3836363">戴维·施威默（David Schwimmer）则要求采取行动，以抗击</a>他的仇恨“ nazi”帖子，争辩说“ nazi”帖子，争辩说“沉默”。</p><p>坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）的邮政在审判中首次出现在<a href="htt